channel.title: Making money off runescape
channel.description:
Hey noobs, yes im going to try to make money off runescape. Well not try anymore, because i have already sold 2 Lvl 3's with 85 mining for 30$ each which is pretty good. Im currently now trying to get some more up with mining but also some other skills now like thieving.
[IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/rh0uw9.png[/img]
Also i have good soul wars bot, firemaker, and some money maker scripts
So im probably going to bot about 100m and get 2 99s per acc and sell them.
But my question for all of you is do you want to be in on this with me? We could maybe even start a site that sells accs and such.
Please dont comment botting is gay or anything negative because ill ask a mod to remove your posts
